{"tid":2015108,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"議會也需要和勇不分","createTime":"2020-05-13T12:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T12:12:37.000Z","uid":57542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9fd70f0e56f50d4597d1ba46deca0e9f9c6d5cb1","tid":2015108,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"議會也需要和勇不分　《香港革新論》共同作者 - 鄺英豪<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;節錄&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n經過去年的街頭運動，民主派陣營對議會抗爭要求提升不少，圍堵主席台算是最低消費，但需要更顯著的突破。無疑，有民主派勇將多番嘗試衝破建制議員夥拍保安的防線，結果勇戰受傷，或者被抬離場。<br />\n<br />\n但是，一部份泛民議員被鏡頭拍到表現「錫身」，前方在打仗，自己卻在會議廳內行行企企，交交戲、打打卡、圍爐交頭接耳，甚至留在座位上直播。等到主席郭榮鏗一句「宣佈結束會議」，之後跟大隊離場。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200512&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20916469\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200512%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20916469&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHN2ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=3e607c98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200512%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20916469&h=d792ef89\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200512&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20916469</a>"},{"pid":"b975b08d093f0377c191ac0add3a18bf2b2ea121","tid":2015108,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:12:37.000Z","msg":"泛民想呃錢，呃選票<br />\n<br />\n冇咁易 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}